          <title>Carson Kelly becomes 1st Cubs player to hit for the cycle in 32 years</title>
          <description><![CDATA[WEST SACRAMENTO, Calif. (AP) — Carson Kelly had come close to hitting for the cycle, yet that elusive triple kept holding him back. He had just two triples over a 10-year big league career before Monday night. That's when Kelly became the first Chicago Cubs player in 32 years to hit for the cycle.]]></description>
